<span id="freeTextContainer14092348718492189599">I&apos;m speechless. For non-Palestinians, it&apos;s important to read this novel since it summarizes the story of Palestine - the story of great love and great loss-.<br/>For Palestinians, it&apos;s good though painful to see our miseries put into words.<br/><br/>May I can write about some points of this outstanding novel ,later.<br/><br/>The lovely signature of my Palestinian sister Susan Abulhawa on my copy of Mornings in Jenin <br/><br/><span>[image error]</span><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1380373911i/727720.jpg' width='320' height='240' alt='IMG410-01' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/> </span>
